				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: haste and slow stacking?<a name="66785"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 13 04 6:17 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>the highest % will be the only one that effects it but secondary effects like damage, resist adjustment they will stick even if a higher % is being used.
<br />

<br />
Instruments do not effect how much haste or slow is made that is hard coded but the secondary effects atk,str whattever will be enhanced. And as far as the instruments in groups it depends greatly on the situation most of the time I am melleing but if I need some songs to be enhancened such as a mez,debuff on a resistant mob or when doing resist songs on raids I am out with the instrument </span></td>
