				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: haste and slow stacking?<a name="67496"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 19 04 3:24 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Er, enchanters don't get snare. It wasn't the snare that was overwritten Largo's, it was the slow. In this case, the slow components occupy the same slots, hence the effect was overwritten and Largo's fades. On a side note, beastlord and shaman slows will also cause Largo's to fade (same slot as enchanter slow, same reason).
<br />

<br />
In the case of the snare component, Largo's is only in conflict with some NPC effects - no PC castable spell has a snare in the same slot as Largo's (with the exception of the snare on the early shaman HoTs Stoicism and Torpor).</span></td>
