				<td colspan="2"><span>Okay, it helps if I actually look at Lucy's once in awhile.
<br />

<br />
/bonk self...again
<br />

<br />
Largo's has slow in slot 2 and snare in slot 3.  Slow spells are slot 2.  Snare spells are slot 2.  That is why the song will drop when other classes land slow on the mob, but it will stay up when other classes land snare, the higher snare taking over of course.
<br />

<br />
Not sure how a fix would work.  All I know is that it is a pain to pull mobs using Largo's if a slowing class lands their spells.  What starts as a nicely staggered pull with plenty of time to mezz the 2nd snared mob ends up w/ a stunned bard and 2 mobs in camp.  At least they both are slowed, heh.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-6.gif" border="0" alt="Sad" hspace="2" /> This is the reason I pull starting w/ mezz now, and only use Largo's to snare fleeing mobs.  </span></td>
